Name:           luna-compiler
Version:        0.1
Stability:      Alpha
Cabal-Version:  >= 1.8
--License-file:   LICENSE
Author:         Flowbox <contact@flowbox.io>
Maintainer:     Flowbox <contact@flowbox.io>
Build-Type:     Simple

Flag Debug
  Description: Enable debug support
  Default:     False


Executable luna
  Main-Is:        Main.hs
  Hs-Source-Dirs: src
  Other-Modules:  Paths_luna_compiler

  if flag(debug)
    GHC-Options:  -csacc
  GHC-Options:    -Wall -O2

  Extensions:     DoAndIfThenElse
                  NoImplicitPrelude
  Build-Depends:  base,
                  containers,
                  flowbox-config,
                  flowbox-utils,
                  luna-core,
                  luna-pass,
                  luna-distribution,
                  luna-initializer,
                  MissingH,
                  optparse-applicative < 0.10, 
                  timeit
-- FIXME: update optparse-applicative to newer version


Test-Suite tests
  Type:           exitcode-stdio-1.0
  Main-Is:        Spec.hs
  Hs-Source-Dirs: src, test
  GHC-Options:    -Wall -threaded -O2
  Extensions:     NoImplicitPrelude
  Build-Depends:  base,
                  flowbox-config,
                  flowbox-utils,
                  hspec,
                  luna-core,
                  luna-initializer,
                  luna-pass,
                  process,
                  raw-strings-qq
